comments: Johnson (LAL) briefly engages with Nnaji (DEN) as he rolls to the basket.
McClung (LAL) jumps from A to B and legally contest the play near the rim by Nnaji (DEN).
Cancar (DEN) is in the paint for at or about three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Cancar (DEN) makes marginal contact with Reaves (LAL) as the pair move up the court, Reaves' reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Gabriel (LAL) makes marginal contact as he briefly places two hands on Cancar's (DEN) body during his drive.
Gabriel (LAL) legally contests the driving shot attempt by Cancar (DEN).
Jones (LAL) jumps from point A to B and makes contact with Howard's (DEN) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Howard (DEN) contest McClung's (LAL) jump shot and gives him room to land following the attempt, McClung extends his leg in an abnormal way, causing the leg to leg contact.
Reaves (LAL) makes contact with the ball last before it goes out of bonds. DEN maintains possession of the ball.
Johnson (LAL) makes marginal contact with Forbes' (DEN) body while attempting to trap the player along the sideline and with his two teammates.
Gabriel (LAL) gives Reed (DEN) room to land on the jump shot attempt.
Howard (DEN) legally contests Reaves' (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Nnaji (DEN) moves towards the basket and makes incidental contact with Jones (LAL) on the sequence.
After the steal and in transition, Reaves (LAL) makes marginal contact to the arm of Reed (DEN).
All Flagrant Fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Johnson (LAL) grabs Cancar's (DEN) jersey off-ball as he is cutting to get open during the inbound play.
McClung (LAL) makes contact with Forbes's (DEN) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Reed (DEN) places his arm on Reaves' (LAL) hip while defending the dribble.
Reed (DEN) gives Reaves (LAL) room to land on the jump shot attempt, additionally the contact to his hand is deemed legal high-five contact.
Cancar (DEN) commits a take foul on Jones (LAL).
Howard (DEN) commits a take foul on Jones (LAL).
Gabriel (LAL) makes foot to foot contact with Howard (DEN), causing him to fall to the ground during the inbound play.
